12.short_description: User Experience (UX) Agency

18.description:
Chocolat·UX User eXperience Research & Design is a specialized agency in Human-Computer Interaction research and in intuitive interactive experiences design.
We help our clients to design and develop intuitive and efficient User Experience (UX) and User Interfaces (UI)
based on science.

We developed a User Experience (UX) model and methodology, based on several scientific disciplines, such as user’s psycho-sociology, behavioral economics, interactive design, usability, and human factors, among others.

Our Services:

User Experience (UX) Consulting:
We test the experience that the users live while they interact with your software, through a rigorous 3 stages science-based methodology:
•Expert Inspection
We make a comprehensive visual and functional analysis of the interfaces of your software to identify its defects and areas of opportunity.
•Usability Testing
We test your software through real users, we record their screen, their facial expressions and their brain activity (EEG), and we interview them to identify the problems and areas of opportunity, and to measure the efficiency and satisfaction level of your product.
•Analysis and Results
We carefully analyze all the data and we deliver you a report with findings, suggestions and corrective mockups. You get a detailed and data supported map to significantly improve your software.

Graphical User Interface Design (UI / GUI):
We design / redesign the graphical user interfaces of your software product through our UX model, this ensures that your software will be highly intuitive, efficient and will deliver an optimal experience to your users.

Software Development:
We design and develop web sites and web apps, online shops, administrative software and mobile applications. We develop based on the User Experience paradigm.

Training:
We create customized User Experience (UX) and Graphic User Interface Design (GUI/UI) workshops for each company's development and design teams.
